title: Beef Borek Filo Snail & Garlic Yoghurt Take your cooking skills to the next level!
description: Time to unleash your inner chef! Unravel the layers of flavour hidden within this dish, with tender, spiced beef encased in crunchy filo. Paired with a carrot salad and a side of tangy garlic yoghurt, this dish is a twist on tradition which is sure to please!
